<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>W. BINNS Plumbing & Heating Engineers</title>
  <meta name="description" content="W. BINNS Plumbing & Heating Engineers. Bathrooms, boilers, heating systems and quality plumbing installations across Kirklees and Calderdale." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f3f3;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --text: #181818;
      --muted: #5f5b5b;
      --line: #e6e1e1;
      --brand: #f51b22;
      --brand-dark: #c41212;
      --accent: #fff4f4;
      --shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(40, 20, 20, 0.08);
      --radius: 20px;
      --max: 1240px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Trebuchet MS", "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 28px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .sticky-band {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      background: rgba(245, 27, 34, 0.98);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }

    .sticky-inner {
      min-height: 76px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 6px 0;
    }

    .top-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .top-actions.right {
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .contact-box {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 42px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 800;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      white-space: nowrap;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .icon {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .logo-wrap {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo-wrap img {
      height: 88px;
      width: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.22));
    }

    .trust-strip {
      background: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .trust-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }

    .trust-item {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #222;
    }

    .trust-item img {
      height: 34px;
      width: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .area-pill {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--brand-dark);
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 30px 0 22px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.02fr 0.98fr;
      gap: 22px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .hero-copy, .hero-photo {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      padding: 34px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      align-self: flex-start;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--brand-dark);
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 60px);
      line-height: 1.03;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 19px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0 0 22px;
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .hero-points {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .pill {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #202020;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      border: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn-primary { background: var(--brand); color: #fff; }
    .btn-secondary { background: #fff; color: #111; border: 1px solid var(--line); }

    .hero-photo img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      min-height: 460px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    section { padding: 24px 0; }

    .section-heading { margin-bottom: 18px; }

    .section-title {
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: 34px;
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }

    .section-copy {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 720px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .services-grid, .job-grid, .contact-grid, .why-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .job-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.9fr; }

    .card, .job-card, .contact-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .card { padding: 24px; }

    .card h3, .job-card-header h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    }

    .card p, .job-card-header p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); }

    .checklist {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .check {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 15px 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .cta-panel {
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .cta-panel h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .cta-panel p {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.86);
    }

    .job-card {
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 22px;
    }

    .job-card-header {
      padding: 18px 20px 8px;
    }

    .job-images {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 14px 16px;
    }

    .job-images.three { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .job-images.single { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

    .job-images img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .contact-cards { display: grid; gap: 12px; }

    .contact-card { padding: 18px; }

    .contact-card strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    form { display: grid; gap: 12px; }

    input, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 15px 16px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font: inherit;
      background: #fff;
    }

    textarea { min-height: 130px; resize: vertical; }

    footer {
      margin-top: 28px;
      padding: 24px 0 34px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .mobile-bar {
      position: fixed;
      left: 12px;
      right: 12px;
      bottom: 12px;
      z-index: 999;
      display: none;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .mobile-bar a { flex: 1; text-align: center; }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .hero-grid, .services-grid, .job-grid, .contact-grid, .why-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .checklist { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .sticky-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .top-actions, .top-actions.right, .trust-inner { justify-content: center; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .checklist, .job-images, .job-images.three {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .logo-wrap img { height: 78px; }
      .hero-copy { padding: 26px; }
      .section-title { font-size: 29px; }
      .hero-photo img { min-height: 300px; }
      .mobile-bar { display: flex; }
      body { padding-bottom: 74px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="sticky-band">
    <div class="container sticky-inner">
      <div class="top-actions left">
        <a class="contact-box" href="tel:+447521913164"><span class="icon">☎</span><span>07521 913 164</span></a>
      </div>
      <a href="#home" class="logo-wrap" aria-label="W. BINNS Plumbing & Heating Engineers home">
        <img src="images/logo.png" alt="W. BINNS Plumbing & Heating Engineers logo" />
      </a>
      <div class="top-actions right">
        <a class="contact-box" href="mailto:cjz1@hotmail.co.uk"><span class="icon">✉</span><span>Email Craig</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="trust-strip">
    <div class="container trust-inner">
      <div class="trust-item"><img src="images/gas-safe.png" alt="Gas Safe logo" /><span>Gas Safe Registered</span></div>
      <div class="trust-item"><img src="images/ideal-logo.png" alt="Ideal Boilers logo" /><span>Ideal Boiler Installations</span></div>
      <div class="area-pill">Kirklees &amp; Calderdale</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="home">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <div class="eyebrow">Bathrooms • Boilers • Heating • Plumbing</div>
          <h1>Proper plumbing and heating work, finished clean.</h1>
          <p class="lead">Craig at W. BINNS Plumbing &amp; Heating Engineers handles bathrooms, boilers, hot water systems and general plumbing across Kirklees and Calderdale, with a tidy finish and no fuss.</p>
          <div class="hero-points">
            <span class="pill">Bathrooms</span>
            <span class="pill">Boilers</span>
            <span class="pill">Heating systems</span>
            <span class="pill">Utility rooms</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#gallery">View work</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#contact">Get a quote</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-photo">
          <img src="images/grey-shower-room.jpg" alt="Grey shower room installation" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <h2 class="section-title">What I do</h2>
          <p class="section-copy">Good workmanship, sensible layouts and a clean final result.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Bathrooms &amp; shower rooms</h3>
            <p>Full installs, showers, trays, enclosures, baths, toilets, basins, towel radiators and smart use of space.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Boilers &amp; hot water</h3>
            <p>Boiler changes, cylinders, plant rooms, copper pipework, upgrades and clean heating layouts built to last.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>General plumbing</h3>
            <p>Utility rooms, taps, sinks, appliances, pipe alterations and the detail work that finishes a job properly.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
      <div class="container why-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="section-title">Why choose W. BINNS</h2>
          <p class="section-copy">Experienced, straightforward and focused on a neat job from start to finish.</p>
          <div class="checklist">
            <div class="check">25 years hands-on experience</div>
            <div class="check">Gas Safe registered</div>
            <div class="check">Tidy pipework and clean finishes</div>
            <div class="check">Kirklees and Calderdale coverage</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-panel">
          <h3>Need a quote?</h3>
          <p>Call or email Craig directly for a quote, advice or to talk through the job.</p>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+447521913164">07521 913 164</a></p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:cjz1@hotmail.co.uk">cjz1@hotmail.co.uk</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="gallery">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <h2 class="section-title">Recent work</h2>
          <p class="section-copy">Grouped properly so each job makes sense at a glance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="job-grid">
          <article class="job-card">
            <div class="job-card-header">
              <h3>Heating plant room installation</h3>
              <p>Two views of a neatly finished boiler and cylinder setup with exposed copper pipework.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="job-images">
              <img src="images/plant-room-1.jpg" alt="Heating plant room view 1" />
              <img src="images/plant-room-2.jpg" alt="Heating plant room view 2" />
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="job-card">
            <div class="job-card-header">
              <h3>Modern tiled bathroom</h3>
              <p>Wall tiling detail and fitted vanity area from the same bathroom job.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="job-images">
              <img src="images/tile-detail.jpg" alt="Bathroom tile detail" />
              <img src="images/vanity-install.jpg" alt="Bathroom vanity installation" />
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="job-card">
            <div class="job-card-header">
              <h3>Concealed hot water and boiler setup</h3>
              <p>Finished cloakroom with hidden cylinder and boiler arranged neatly behind sliding doors.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="job-images three">
              <img src="images/cloakroom-finish.jpg" alt="Cloakroom finished view" />
              <img src="images/cylinder-cupboard.jpg" alt="Cylinder cupboard" />
              <img src="images/boiler-cupboard.jpg" alt="Boiler cupboard" />
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="job-card">
            <div class="job-card-header">
              <h3>Grey shower room and fitted furniture</h3>
              <p>Matching shower enclosure and fitted vanity furniture from the same grey bathroom project.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="job-images">
              <img src="images/grey-shower-room.jpg" alt="Grey shower room" />
              <img src="images/grey-fitted-furniture.jpg" alt="Grey fitted furniture" />
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="job-card">
            <div class="job-card-header">
              <h3>Feature ensuite shower room</h3>
              <p>Bold blue tiling and curved enclosure for a more characterful finish.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="job-images">
              <img src="images/curved-shower-room.jpg" alt="Curved shower room" />
              <img src="images/blue-feature-ensuite.jpg" alt="Blue feature ensuite" />
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="job-card">
            <div class="job-card-header">
              <h3>Bath installation</h3>
              <p>Clean bath fit with feature tile strip and crisp final finish.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="job-images single">
              <img src="images/bath-installation.jpg" alt="Bath installation" />
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
      <div class="container contact-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="section-title">Get in touch</h2>
          <p class="section-copy">Use the form below or tap the phone and email boxes above.</p>
          <form action="mailto:cjz1@hotmail.co.uk" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your name" required />
            <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone number" required />
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email address" />
            <textarea name="message" placeholder="Tell me about the job"></textarea>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Send enquiry</button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-cards">
          <a class="contact-card" href="tel:+447521913164"><strong>Phone</strong>07521 913 164</a>
          <a class="contact-card" href="mailto:cjz1@hotmail.co.uk"><strong>Email</strong>cjz1@hotmail.co.uk</a>
          <div class="contact-card"><strong>Area covered</strong>Kirklees and Calderdale</div>
          <div class="contact-card"><strong>About Craig</strong>Time served plumbing and heating engineer. Gas Safe registered. 25 years experience.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <strong>W. BINNS Plumbing &amp; Heating Engineers</strong><br />
      Plumbing, heating and bathrooms across Kirklees and Calderdale.
    </div>
  </footer>

  <div class="mobile-bar">
    <a class="contact-box" href="tel:+447521913164"><span class="icon">☎</span><span>Call</span></a>
    <a class="contact-box" href="mailto:cjz1@hotmail.co.uk"><span class="icon">✉</span><span>Email</span></a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
